Package: postshock
Type: Package
Title: Post-Shock Forecasting with an Intercept Correction Modeling Framework
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    c(
      person("Qiyang", "Wang", email = "qiyangw3@illinois.edu", role = c("aut","cre")),
      person("Daniel J.", "Eck", email = "dje13@illinois.edu", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Implements donor balancing weights (DBW) and related utilities
    for post-shock time-series forecasting. The methods estimate a post-shock
    intercept-correction term using information aggregated from donor series.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
